name: FIRST 787-10 IN CALGARY! KLM Boeing 787-10 Dreamliner Takeoff
description:
Thank you to RadarBox for supporting this plane spotting video! Find out more about them at https://www.radarbox.com/?referrer=AlexAviation

On Friday, KLM sent their Boeing 787-10 to Calgary for the very first time, on a rare equipment swap. This also marks the first ever visit of the 787-10 in Calgary, as we only see regular flights with the 787-9 and the occasional 787-8.

Great to see it here and in the KLM livery, hopefully there'll be many more visits in the future!
